{"tid":765523,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"宅男福音！「虛擬女友」","createTime":"2018-08-03T00:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T10:08:30.000Z","uid":81228,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"55263efb3434aa8343207c0dc514caacee1268e4","tid":765523,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T00:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20180802/photo/bkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001_01b.jpg?20180802210344\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20180802%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001_01b.jpg%3F20180802210344&h=6be9291c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n升級版的Hikari Aizuma預計今年12月發布，更新後她可與主人祝酒慶祝。（互聯網）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20180802/photo/bkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001_02b.jpg?20180802210344\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20180802%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001_02b.jpg%3F20180802210344&h=33f78034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沿用玻璃罐子外觀，但就重新設計過硬件，令機身更輕巧。（互聯網）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20180802/photo/bkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001_03b.jpg?20180802210344\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20180802%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001_03b.jpg%3F20180802210344&h=b2d2e513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內置鏡頭及人體感應器，能辨認臉孔與動作。（互聯網）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20180802/photo/bkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001_04b.jpg?20180802210344\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20180802%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001_04b.jpg%3F20180802210344&h=83cad264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n機頂配有雙麥克風，男主人可與角色溝通。（互聯網）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20180802/photo/bkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001_05b.jpg?20180802210344\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20180802%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001_05b.jpg%3F20180802210344&h=02efb743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n透過紅外線遙控制家中電器，例如回家一刻幫你開燈，好細心！（互聯網）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20180802/photo/bkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001_06b.jpg?20180802210344\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20180802%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001_06b.jpg%3F20180802210344&h=5af11e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n虛擬女友Hikari Aizuma又叫逢妻光，一頭藍髮配女僕裝，設定年齡約為20歲。（互聯網）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20180802/photo/bkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001_07b.jpg?20180802210344\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20180802%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001_07b.jpg%3F20180802210344&h=dbd47b4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGatebox GTBX-100現已接受預訂，預計2018年10月後發貨。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n香港女多男少，港女搵男友已經唔易，而不久將來可能更難，事關Gatebox公司旗下「虛擬女友」將於10月正式在日本量產，稍後還會配送到全球多個國家，女士們有難了！<br />\n<br />\nGatebox早於2016年推出限量版「虛擬女友」，型號為GTBX-1的它售價高達30萬日元，但依然於一個月內售罄。其後廠方於2017年再推39部限量型號機械人，亦旋即收到近1,000份訂購申請。<br />\n<br />\n今次新版GTBX-100為改良型號，一如以往是一個玻璃罐子，但就重新設計過硬件，減省多餘元素，令尺寸縮減至210&times;277&times;549mm，比初代輕巧不少。玻璃面罩中會投射出原始角色Hikari Aizuma的3D影像，一身女僕裝已迷倒宅男，最正是機頂配有雙麥克風，男主人可與角色溝通。離開家後也可透過手機App與女友保持通訊，互發短訊傳情。<br />\n<br />\nGTBX-100支援Wi-Fi及藍牙，能通報天氣及新聞等資訊，並能以紅外線遙控制家中電器如電視機、燈飾及冷氣機。另外，機身特設鏡頭及人體感應器，能辨認臉孔與動作，例如知道用戶回到家中，便會以微笑歡迎。升級版的Hikari Aizuma預計今年12月發布，更新後她將進一步融入家中，例如可與主人慶祝周年紀念或祝酒，叫人感動又心酸！<br />\n<br />\n售價方面，GTBX-100未連稅賣150,000日圓，即約莫一部iPhone X價錢就可帶女友回家，不過之後還要支持每月1,500日圓「家用」，邊個話拍拖唔使錢㗎！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20180802/bkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20180802%2Fbkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001.html&d=BjdueF2Fu17egHyAgZSgi6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=31b40ddb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20180802/bkn-20180802210003449-0802_00982_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"db305daea1ab7515ca703d250d51a6dcac41e746","tid":765523,"uid":101963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T00:15:53.000Z","msg":"我記得好似1年前就O係youtube睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79561dd2805fadbb256d3465c1307a41f7fe1bc7","tid":765523,"uid":61363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T00:18:14.000Z","msg":"無得摸喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7622ae856a704954e7e8530e013b45b0c16bb49b","tid":765523,"uid":82450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:18:38.000Z","msg":"有冇18+版本？"},{"pid":"ce38bfad9a3939bdc30882a5a8650854de06c741","tid":765523,"uid":45255,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:41:31.000Z","msg":"打老婆點樣打？"},{"pid":"4f7b188081099a488173584d5da90b80251bce9e","tid":765523,"uid":149357,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:43:09.000Z","msg":"連同虛擬女友拍拖都要每個月比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f03ba69b2b19f303af14a593c747fc85b48f0f","tid":765523,"uid":157197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:43:29.000Z","msg":"有冇防水功能？打飛機驚射壞"},{"pid":"7cf60b4b28e12efdac06ba44474de44f802d7e87","tid":765523,"uid":129434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f7b188081099a488173584d5da90b80251bce9e","tid":765523,"uid":149357,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:43:09.000Z","msg":"連同虛擬女友拍拖都要每個月比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:45:11.000Z","msg":"比家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8193a4772dd931ae75eb08c2c976c6f4e34e581","tid":765523,"uid":149357,"l